# UI / Design system

Single locked theme **"Suar Dermaga" (Ombak v2 тАФ harbor light over the ledger)**: the warm-paper
"Ledger on Paper" base kept verbatim (hairline structure, borders over shadows, teal accent,
Plus Jakarta Sans + Geist Mono), evolved with a **sea-glass horizon wash**, a **navy "hull at
dusk" sidebar** (hue locked тЙд252 тАФ never purple), an amber **suar/beacon** attention system, and
the **Pandu** assistant pattern. Tokens (OKLCH) live in `apps/web/src/styles/globals.css` тАФ
light + dark via `next-themes`. Change the accent only via `--primary`/`--ring`/`--sidebar-*`.

**Suar Dermaga specifics (on top of Ledger on Paper):**

- **`--sea-glass`** is the ONLY "water" fill: the dashboard `horizon-wash` utility (shell `<main>`
  only; cards stay pure white) and Pandu surfaces. Never a card/table background.
- **Split neutrals stay**: `--secondary`/`--muted`/`--accent` distinct; `--border` тЙа `--input`.
- **Signed numerics**: `--signed-up`/`--signed-down` via **`NumberDelta`**; losses/negative
  margins use `text-signed-down`, NEVER `text-destructive` (destructive = app failure only).
- **Status colors come ONLY from `StatusBadge`/`STATUS_BADGE_TONES`** (`components/status-badge.tsx`):
  tones ok/info/warn/urgent/danger/neutral over `--status-ok/info/warn`, `--highlight(+-strong)`,
  `--destructive`. No raw Tailwind palette (emerald/amber/sky/rose) for status тАФ dark mode comes
  free from tokens. Warn callout trio: `border-highlight/40 bg-highlight/15 text-status-warn`;
  ok trio: `border-status-ok/30 bg-status-ok/10 text-status-ok`. Exception: permanent dark camera
  surfaces (mobile scanner overlay, video stage) may keep their raw dark-surface colors.
- **`num`** (mono+tabular) on EVERY number/code the user reads тАФ stock, money, qty, resi, SKU
  codes, counts. **`num-display`** (mono 28px w700) = hero numerals (StatCard value, POS total).
- **`eyebrow`** micro-caps for section/stat/nav labels (never paired with another `text-*` size).
- **Elevation = hairline**: no shadows on cards; shadows only on true overlays.
- **Motion**: `--ease-tide` for entrances/dock; skeleton = `shimmer-water` (not pulse); a GLOBAL
  `prefers-reduced-motion` guard lives in globals.css; JS-driven motion (recharts) must also gate
  via **`useReducedMotion`** тЖТ `isAnimationActive={!reducedMotion}`.
- **Maritime budget**: `WaveHairline` (riak divider) ONLY at hero/landing/auth section breaks;
  `LighthouseArt` + "Suar" voice only on error/404 routes; maritime words appear as eyebrows
  ("Anjungan") тАФ primary nav labels stay functional. Tables/badges/forms are motif-free.

## Brand chrome

- **`BrandMark`/`BrandBadge`** (`components/brand-mark.tsx`) тАФ the falcon-eye-over-riak mark; the
  ONLY brand mark (never an inline letter chip). Favicon `app/icon.svg`, `apple-icon.tsx`,
  `opengraph-image.tsx` (+ data-free variant for `/share/[token]` тАФ resi must never leak into
  link previews), `manifest.ts`, `robots.ts`, `<html lang="id">`, `metadataBase` from
  `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL`, viewport themeColor pair.
- **Branded failure routes**: `app/not-found.tsx`, `app/error.tsx`, `app/global-error.tsx`,
  `app/(dashboard)/error.tsx` (keeps the shell frame), route `loading.tsx` (incl. the share
  page). Calm "Suar" voice + lighthouse art + a way back. Never ship a route that can fall
  through to an unbranded Next default.

## Pandu (assistant) pattern тАФ honesty is a hard rule

- **`PanduDock`** (`components/pandu/`): bottom-right pill тЖТ sea-glass card; suppressed on
  `/recordings`, `/dashboard/sales/new`, `/dashboard/purchasing/new`. Hero NL bar on the
  dashboard only. Both route through **`routePanduQuery`** (keyword тЖТ existing URL filters).
- **Stub contract (jujur)**: nudges (`usePanduNudges`) are deterministic rules over queries that
  already exist тАФ real numbers, rule-ranked, max 3, labeled "otomatis"; the card carries a
  permanent "Pratinjau" label; no generated prose, EVER, until the real AI lands. Dismissals
  persist per nudge-id (`store/pandu-store.ts`) and re-arm when the datum changes.

